&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; But the link of stateB is going to be a fixed link, right?
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; So how would this work if somehow user knew the link of StateB (say by
